{
  "stem": "9963.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Next day, the-- the police were there, and the mayor with the principal and all the teachers with the parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we told them what's happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So over there in Poland, the principal, he had the right to really beat up on the boys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if they didn't behave, they took him into his office, and he really punished him very seriously.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was the time-- and that principal, he was a very righteous man, a very nice person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He's seen, you know, the thing what they did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he really punished them very seriously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Since then, we had to live with peace.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't have to fight for our rights.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you learn the ABC.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first years, you learn the ABC.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you progressing where you're going, higher and higher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- it's-- the thing is within Europe, a boy you had to learn very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For instance, in the morning we-- we went to Polish school at 7:30 to 1 o'clock in the afternoon. 1 o'clock, we came home, I ate lunch, and I went back to the Jewish school till 8 o'clock in the evening. 8 O'clock in the evening when we come home, sometimes I could eat, or sometimes I was so tired that I couldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to bed, and I got up about 3 o'clock in the morning to make my homework to the Polish school.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a constant thing day in and day out, seven days a week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have any rest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only rest, what it was actually was a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, we had to go to the synagogue in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in afternoon, we had to go to the Jewish school to learn for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
